Docker networks 
to communcate docker to docker or stop communication in between docker will use docker networks 
4 types 
1)bridge   - its default network while create containers
2)host
3)none
4)overlay 
docker network ls --- to check list of networks

create 2 to 3 containers
cmd : docker inspect cont1   --- to know about particular object (ex : container)
docker inspect cont1 | -i "network" / docker inspect cont1 | grep -i "ip"  -- to get particular details
now we have to check either ex 2nd container ip pinging in 1st container, 1st conatiner ip pinging in 2nd container
will do in two ways
inside conatiner & outside container also
docker exec -it cont1 ping 172.17.0.3
docker exec -it cont1 touch filename ---- to create a file
docker exec -it cont1 mkdir sree  -- to creat folder 







